BOARD OF DIRECTORS RESOLUTION
{{ named_insured | upper }}

===============================================================================

RESOLVED, that the Board of Directors of {{ named_insured }} (the "Company"),
a {{ entity_type }} organized under the laws of the State of {{ state_of_incorporation }},
at a duly convened meeting held on {{ resolution_date | default("January 15, 2026") }},
at which a quorum was present and acting, hereby adopts the following resolutions:

===============================================================================
BOARD COMPOSITION
===============================================================================

Total Board Members:        {{ board_size }}
Independent Directors:      {{ independent_directors }}
Inside Directors:           {{ board_size - independent_directors }}

DIRECTORS:
{% for member in board_members %}
  {{ loop.index }}. {{ member.name }}
     Title:        {{ member.title }}
     Independent:  {{ "Yes" if member.is_independent else "No" }}
     Committee:    {{ member.committee | default("None") }}
{% if member.shares_owned %}     Shares Owned:  {{ member.shares_owned }}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

===============================================================================
COMMITTEE STRUCTURE
===============================================================================

Audit Committee:
{% for member in board_members if member.committee and "Audit" in member.committee %}
  - {{ member.name }} ({{ member.title }}){% if loop.first %} — Committee Chair{% endif %}
{% else %}
  (No audit committee members listed)
{% endfor %}

Financial Expert on Audit Committee: {{ "Yes" if audit_committee_financial_expert else "No" }}

===============================================================================
DIRECTORS AND OFFICERS LIABILITY INSURANCE
===============================================================================

RESOLVED, that the officers of the Company are hereby authorized and directed
to procure Directors and Officers Liability Insurance on behalf of the Company
and its directors and officers, with limits of liability not to exceed
{{ limits_requested | currency }} and a retention of {{ retention_requested | currency }},
for the policy period {{ effective_date }} through {{ expiration_date }}.

RESOLVED, that the Secretary is directed to maintain a copy of this resolution
with the corporate records.

===============================================================================

I, the undersigned Secretary of {{ named_insured }}, do hereby certify that
the foregoing is a true and correct copy of the resolutions adopted by the
Board of Directors at its meeting on {{ resolution_date | default("January 15, 2026") }}.

